dc_title_s: Park and Ride Lots, San Francisco Bay Area, 2007
dc_description_s: This point shapefile contains the locations of park and ride lots in the San Francisco Bay Area of California. This layer is part of the Bay Area Metropolitan Transportation Commission (MTC) GIS Maps and Data collection. This dataset is intended for researchers, students, and policy makers for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data. California, Metropolitan Transportation Commission. (2007). Park and Ride Lots, San Francisco Bay Area, 2007, MTC. Available at: http://purl.stanford.edu/xp514zq9070.
